sequenceDiagram
    actor User as User/Gateway
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant Check as quota callback
    participant DB as instances table
    participant Net as network helper
    participant Docker as DockerHelper
    participant Engine as Docker Engine

    User->>API: POST /instance
    API->>Check: allow / deny
    Check-->>API: result
    API->>DB: insert status=creating
    API->>Net: get project network name
    API->>Docker: create_container(...)
    Docker->>Engine: pull image + run container
    Engine-->>Docker: container_id + runtime status
    Docker-->>API: runtime metadata
    API->>DB: update status=running
    API-->>User: 201 Created
